  lines:
  - speaker: BOSS
    text: Latte, keep the apartment tidy while I am away.
  - speaker: LATTE
    text: The cameras are watching. I can still fix a few things.
  - speaker: BOSS
    text: Start with the shoes, then return my pillow.
